data.title: College of Liberal Arts and Sciences Laboratory Operations and Resources
data.meta_description: Explore a variety of licensed software available to GVSU students, faculty, and staff.
data.text:
Other Licensed Software

Below is a list of other department licensed software that may be available for students to use. If you would like to request access to one or more, click the Laboratory Software Request Form button to submit a request form.

Laboratory Software Request Form

Students: Login with your GVSU Username followed by '@student'. For example, John Smith would log in with 'smithj@student'

Faculty/Staff: Login with your normal GVSU Username. For example, Jane Smith would log in with 'smithja'.

**In order to access off campus, you may need to use VPN.
